OL,3,CRare albino buffalo nicknamed 'Donald
OL,4,CTrump' spared from Eid sacrifice
OL,6,FA rare albino buffalo that became a
OL,7,Fviral sensation for its uncanny
OL,8,Fresemblance to US President Donald
OL,9,FTrump has been saved from being
OL,10,Fslaughtered in a last-minute
OL,11,Fintervention.
OL,13,FPeople in Bangladesh flocked to take
OL,14,Fpictures of the buffalo, which gained
OL,15,Finternet fame due to its flowing tuft
OL,16,Fof blond hair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
