PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780009385
OL,3,CRare albino buffalo nicknamed 'Donald
OL,4,CTrump' spared from Eid sacrifice
OL,6,FFarmer Zia Uddin Mridha, 38, said his
OL,7,Fbrother nicknamed the buffalo Donald
OL,8,FTrump due to its "extraordinary hair",
OL,9,Fbut said the similarities with the
OL,10,Fpresident ended there. "The only
OL,11,Fluxury he enjoys is bathing four times
OL,12,Fa day," he added.
OL,14,FThe buffalo, raised at a farm in the
OL,15,Ftown of Narayanganj, drew in a
OL,16,Fconstant stream of social media fans,
OL,17,Fchildren and curious onlookers eager
OL,18,Fto visit the 700-kilogramme creature `
OL,19,Fbut people soon realised the fate that
OL,20,Fawaited it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
