OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780009385
OL,3,CRare albino buffalo nicknamed 'Donald
OL,4,CTrump' spared from Eid sacrifice
OL,6,F'Trump' buffalo spared sacrifice, sent
OL,7,Fto Bangladesh zoo
OL,9,FThe animal was due to be sacrificed
OL,10,Ffor the Islamic festival of Eid al-
OL,11,FAdha (the Feast of the Sacrifice)
OL,12,Fafter being sold to a buyer, until
OL,13,FBangladesh's home minister, Salahuddin
OL,14,FAhmed, stepped in.
OL,16,FAccording to local reports, Ahmed
OL,17,Fordered the release of the buffalo due
OL,18,Fto "security concerns" and for the
OL,19,Fbuyer to be compensated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780009385
OL,3,CRare albino buffalo nicknamed 'Donald
OL,4,CTrump' spared from Eid sacrifice
OL,6,FIn a statement reported by Bengali
OL,7,Fnewspaper Prothom Alo, a police
OL,8,Fofficer said: "Instructions have come
OL,9,Ffrom the top that the buffalo cannot
OL,10,Fbe sacrificed. For now, we have been
OL,11,Ftold to take it to the police station."
OL,13,FThe buffalo's buyer told local media:
OL,14,F"People from the police station came
OL,15,Fand said the government would take it.
OL,16,FWe do not want any disorder. The
OL,17,Fgovernment wanted it, so we handed it
OL,18,Fover.
OL,26,@pD@OOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
