OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780009385
OL,3,CRare albino buffalo nicknamed 'Donald
OL,4,CTrump' spared from Eid sacrifice
OL,6,F"The government said they would pay us
OL,7,Fwhatever price it is worth, or else
OL,8,Fthey would provide a cow for
OL,9,Fsacrifice."
OL,11,FThe buffalo has since been transferred
OL,12,Fto its new home at the Bangladesh
OL,13,FNational Zoo in the country's capital
OL,14,Fof Dhaka.
